INPUT
--> [Delayer
      delay: 20
      mix: % 80
    ]
--> [Saturator
      gain: dB 9.5
    ]
--> [LowPass
      high_cut: % 20
    ]
--> [OverDriver
      threshold: dB -30
      mix: % 100
    ]
--> [Multiplier
      gain: dB 20
    ]
--> [Compressor
      ratio: 10
      threshold: dB -10
      attack: % 5
      mix: % 70
    ]
--> OUTPUT

Simple distortion simulator
